Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:41.02,Title,,0,0,0,,弓矢的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的已经是最高时速了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要怪就怪你的摩托坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,接你的时候顺便在宫城基地发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个铁人的说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你专心开车就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,松手  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,放手  很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种外行看不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的和美禄有血缘关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有相信你是我弟弟的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的云游商人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,做了这么多怎么可能不求回报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点上你是说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只有傻子才会为别人去拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到霜吹驻军地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的部下在那里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄  我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前一定要平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们都活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,伤得好重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看来机械玩偶一爆炸  世界就毁灭了的传说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是童话故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我从那个铁人中感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,许多古人苦苦追求的  一种近乎执念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,执念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那压倒性的力量了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不单单是金属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它能锈蚀所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,植物  动物还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,锈蚀到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛既是支配万物的恐怖之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也是无法对抗的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要说的话就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然而食锈却可以吞噬锈蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,它能利用锈蚀支配生命的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果锈蚀是死神的话  那食锈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,简单来说  就是死神克星了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,锈蚀和蕈菇的力量之间  是否存在某种关联呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过肯定的是  蕈菇是跟着锈蚀进化的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(650,715)}他们在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(650,715)}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口很深  暂时你要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道那东西会往哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我刚才看到了他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是孤独的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会回忌滨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这次别死了  毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可还没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的灵魂存续下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这小子的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(640,715)}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  来算总账吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,商人的话就赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有个大的不得了的巨人往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹  那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过也没听说过那种怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是铁人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,骨骼的形状和这个镇子一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是活着的铁人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,距离多远?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大概三千米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,前进方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,径直朝我们这边走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不做些什么的话  镇子会被毁掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,难道要和它战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能打得过那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个镇子可是祖辈们守下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们离开镇子吧  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,幸助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都理解你不希望这个镇子被毁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔贝罗的灵魂在我们身上  而不在镇子上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,镇子无论被摧毁多少次  也能够重建起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有你和我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,自从见过赤星后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子说话硬气多了啊  幸助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听好  准备开撤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人都不准死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停  都跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的镇子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来拖住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算去死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能去  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去展现一下卡尔贝罗渔夫的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边  大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔贝罗最好的鱼叉手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,白鲸钓手纳兹来会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,冲我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看我一叉子叫你上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才打不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以跑来欺负小孩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,白熊猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…美禄吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无论金钱还是权力  乃至强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,最终都没能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但你放心  黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我来跟你彻底做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  让我们继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,白…白熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我看到了卡尔贝罗渔夫的真正胆力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你去保护大家  趁现在赶紧逃远一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们趁这个时候逃去高台那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么只有熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星怎么没来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,滋露…你们怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑去大路上时  碰巧遇上了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,托她们的福  我好好休息了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你真的还活着呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害啊  熊猫小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿再叙旧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,忌滨自警团来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩交给他们保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:13:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,外面是不是有些吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听说自警团倾巢出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,反正又是在搞演习之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个  别摸鱼好好干活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出大事了  快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点  美禄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  有东西要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不好的预感  离它远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋  只能这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,差一点都能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,红色的药剂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是毘沙门菇毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体是吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是毕斯可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你还会阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,替我照顾好帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了这一炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你该长点记性了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,熊猫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄  不要冲动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我还站着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可之前也是这种心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我可以射箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,像毕斯可一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在黄泉的跟前  我听到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,射箭有两个要领
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是要仔细观察
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个是相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  弓矢的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你会射中的  毕斯可
